Empress Njamah has recounted the traumatic experience she had with her ex-fiance Josh ‘Babybrother’ Wade, who released her nudes after attempts to blackmail her failed. The actress said he did a lot of damage to her and to other women whose nudes he had too. She also revealed that after he took control of her accounts, he used it to reach out to women to dupe and blackmail them. She said she lived in fear of him for a long time until she finally escaped. This is when he began releasing her nudes after seizing her phones, passport, cars and valuables worth millions. She added that Josh, a Liberian national, has been to Kirikiri prison before and is not a new offender in Nigeria. The actress said the appropriate authorities are now handling the matter. She then thanked those who stood by her during the ordeal. See below.